props.lines: The line declaration specifies the minimum height of the item and can also be controlled from v-list with the same prop.
props.loading: Likely indicates a loading state for the treeview item.
props.nav: Reduces the width v-list-item takes up as well as adding a border radius.
props.slim: Probably reduces the vertical padding or height of the treeview item, making it more compact.
props.toggle-icon: Allows customization of the icon used to toggle the expansion and collapse of treeview branches.

events.clickOnce: This event might trigger a specific action when the treeview item is clicked once, as opposed to multiple clicks.
